{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b2c3d4e5-f6a7-8901-bcde-fa2345678901",
    "name": "Payment Gateway \u2014 Third-Party Bulk API",
    "description": "Third-party data access API for the Multi-Tenant Payment Gateway.\n\n## Authentication\nThis collection uses **OAuth 2.0 Client Credentials Flow** (RFC 6749).\n\n### Setup\n1. Set your `client_id` and `client_secret` in the **Variables** tab of this collection\n2. The collection automatically obtains and refreshes the access token\n3. All requests automatically include the `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header\n\n### Token Endpoint\n- **URL**: `{{base_url}}/api/v1/oauth/token`\n- **Method**: POST\n- **Grant Type**: `client_credentials`\n\n### Required Headers on Data Endpoints\n- `Authorization: Bearer <access_token>` (auto-managed by collection auth)\n- `X-Merchant-UUID: <merchant_uuid_string>` (set per-request or via variable)\n\n### Pagination\nAll list endpoints use **cursor-based pagination**:\n- Use `cursor` query param (returned as `next_cursor` in response)\n- `limit`: 1\u2013500 (default 100)\n- `include_count: true` to get total count (slower)\n\n### Rate Limiting\nResponses include rate limit headers:\n- `X-RateLimit-Limit`: Max requests per window\n- `X-RateLimit-Remaining`: Remaining requests\n- `X-RateLimit-Reset`: Window reset timestamp",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
